Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:48.16,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Day by day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:51.89,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うんざりだよね  だから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.08,0:01:56.68,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂々と断っちゃう　キミになりなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.86,0:01:57.89,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my boy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.11,0:02:01.53,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キッパリしなきゃ　嘘に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:06.60,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,付きあってられないよ　狭い世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.11,0:02:09.16,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自分で見つけた　myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:11.50,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好きになって当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:13.96,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,くだらないやり方蹴って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:18.93,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すべてはあたしが決める!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:21.35,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(I say,I say my heaven)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.56,0:02:23.85,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Super Driver　突進まかせて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:25.77,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なんてったって前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.80,0:02:27.58,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不可能！」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:28.72,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(Don't you stop me)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:30.89,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛び越えて　Take it eazy,Go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:33.41,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大勝利って同感もちろん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:35.31,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうなったって快感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:37.03,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「反省会？」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:38.40,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(Get back to wild)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:40.44,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それより　さあ　急いでよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:45.07,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あれもこれも未体験　いつだってムリヤリ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:49.98,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まるでまるで未経験　これからしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:54.71,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あれもこれも未体験　いつだってトツゼン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:59.52,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まるでまるで未経験　それがどうしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:48.16,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Day by day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:51.89,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為無聊之極
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.08,0:01:56.68,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才必須堂堂正正地拒絕　如你一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.86,0:01:57.89,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my boy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.11,0:02:01.53,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須對謊話斬釘截鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:06.60,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這不能相處的狹窄世界內
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.11,0:02:09.16,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現自己　myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:11.50,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然會喜歡上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:13.96,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把無聊的東西一腳踢開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:18.93,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都由我來決定！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:21.35,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(I say,I say my heaven)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.56,0:02:23.85,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Super Driver　隨我衝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:25.77,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管一切向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.80,0:02:27.58,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不可能！」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:28.72,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(Don't you stop me)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:30.89,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們來飛越　Take it eazy,Go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:33.41,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是取得大勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:35.31,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法阻擋的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:37.03,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「反省會？」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:38.40,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(Get back to wild)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:40.44,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個　來吧　加速吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:45.07,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個那個也還沒體驗　無論何時都要硬幹下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:49.98,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完完全全地沒有經驗　現在就去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:54.71,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個那個也還沒體驗　無論何時都要馬上行動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:59.52,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完完全全地沒有經驗　那又怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.88,0:23:45.05,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}空から落ちてきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.26,0:23:47.86,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}全ての願いを乗せて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.90,0:23:52.43,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ひとつの星にはちょっと重かったかな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.08,0:23:55.66,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}やっぱり何かヘンだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.78,0:23:58.27,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}心のキミが消えた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.47,0:24:02.62,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}確かに憶えてるって言えるのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.75,0:24:04.10,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}止マレ！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.26,0:24:07.89,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}過去は自分のもの
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.05,0:24:12.35,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}当然　誰とも取り替えたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.61,0:24:13.56,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}なぜなら…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.77,0:24:18.72,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}バースデイだった　私達には
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.95,0:24:21.69,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}出会いが生まれたときに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.89,0:24:24.07,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}初めての夢が見える
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.23,0:24:29.05,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}どうしようかって　悩んだ事も
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.43,0:24:33.02,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}いま思えば笑えるほどだったよね
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.15,0:24:37.89,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もう忘れてた　キミを探そう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.88,0:23:45.05,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}僅僅只因從天而降
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.26,0:23:47.86,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}便要承擔全部願望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.90,0:23:52.43,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}對於一顆小小流星　是否有些沉重？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.08,0:23:55.66,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}果然有哪裡出了錯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.78,0:23:58.27,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}心中你已消失不見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.47,0:24:02.62,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}「沒忘掉你」這話　又要怎麼說出？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.75,0:24:04.10,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}停下吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.26,0:24:07.89,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}過去只屬於自己
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.05,0:24:12.35,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}當然不會將其交給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.61,0:24:13.56,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}為什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.77,0:24:18.72,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}生日那一天　大家在此處相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.95,0:24:21.69,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}但在那天的初夢前
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.89,0:24:24.07,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我們早已相知相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.23,0:24:29.05,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}之前那不知如何是好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.43,0:24:33.02,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}此刻回想　卻是那般可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.15,0:24:37.89,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}已經忘了嗎　那來找你囉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.26,0:00:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一個慵懶  而又正常到了極點的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.96,0:00:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盂蘭盆會後的盛夏的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視中正在播放的  是跟我一點關係都沒有的同縣選手的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:26.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出於對弱者的同情心  我不由得支持著正處於落後的一方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這時手機卻大聲嚷嚷了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.39,0:00:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是春日啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.41,0:00:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天很閒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.57,0:00:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩點整全員在車站前集合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.70,0:00:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕描淡寫地掛斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.92,0:00:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼就知道我今天很閒的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.47,0:00:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此我可也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…  雖說我什麼計劃也沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:00:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.18,0:01:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘跟你說了  帶一套泳裝騎車過來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.21,0:01:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  帶上足夠的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.22,0:01:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上  Over～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好煩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.57,0:01:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.12,0:01:14.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打手現正悠閒地跑向三壘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:17.91,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投手鈴木  在投手丘上一副崩潰的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:20.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是慘不忍睹的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.67,0:01:21.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真淒慘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.48,0:01:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  沒有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.70,0:01:29.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人向投手鈴木發出噓聲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:32.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就是8：0了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:35.26,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽進入了艱巨的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:14.44,staffbiaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\fn方正黑体_GBK\pos(235,294)\fs27\an5}Endless Eight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:14.44,staffbiaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\fn方正黑体_GBK\pos(235,370)\an5}漫無止境的八月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了  阿虛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多拿點幹勁出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然讓本團長等你  你以為自己是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:23.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要懲罰啦  懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明就提前了15分鐘來  為什麼每次都是最後啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  全都到齊了  出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古泉  你就載實玖瑠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和有希坐阿虛後面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姑且問一句  去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.88,0:03:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是去市民游泳池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天當然要有夏天的樣子  要做有夏天特色的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的時間可是一去不返的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:04:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在就要行動  在這個只有一次的高一的暑假裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的時間啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這消毒液的氣味  真給人一種實在的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來～啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:28.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（禁止跳水  危險！）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊過來  水溫溫的很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙就看不見到處貼的那些禁止跳水的文字說明嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過很讓人欣慰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得  涼宮同學也學會了有常識性的娛樂方法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然打個電話過來  單方面地說好就掛的邀請方式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在不能說得上是常識性的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  笑得那麼開心的涼宮同學  是不會做什麼震動這個世界的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是那樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心  自從上次合宿以來  也沒引起過什麼讓人注目的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這會兒  對涼宮同學而言也好  對我們來說也好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界就是和平的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.64,0:05:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是  實玖瑠親手做的三明治哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝稱讚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再吃一塊炸雞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.07,0:05:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠  給我倒茶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實  非常和平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:43.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說是市民泳池  倒是個更適合平民泳池這名字的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  實玖瑠你在幹什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:05:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種過暑假的方法倒也不賴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些就是我的團員們  說什麼都會聽的  所以隨便吩咐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試著考慮了下今後的活動計劃  如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎樣來度過已經所剩無幾的暑假的計劃表
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOS團的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  暑假只剩下兩週了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得還有很多事情沒做呢  要一起都做完哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  在暑假不能不做的事情…嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏期合宿  游泳池  盆舞  煙火匯演  打工  天體觀測…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個表上的東西要在兩週之內都做完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有別的想要做的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  我想撈金魚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  撈金魚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼明天開始實行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近有什麼地方明天會跳盆舞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有煙火匯演也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少查過了再給我實行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去查吧  回頭聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  別忘了撈金魚哦  這可是實玖瑠的強烈要求哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:19.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼總是我付錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你遲到了  這是當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天可別讓人等了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  今天就此解散
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  現在開始每天都玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天早晨  將我的懶覺奪走的又是春日打來的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到跳盆舞的會場了  時間是今晚  地點是市民運動場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:01.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧她能時機正好地找到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心中正半懷佩服時  春日說出了這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去買浴衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠和有希都說沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買一整套的話就會便宜  我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.71,0:08:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日擅自為朝比奈學姐和長門挑選了以後  毫不客氣地衝進了試衣間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可相當花時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期間頻遭女性顧客冷眼  我們等了大約一小時  三個人終於都換好出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  都非常合適哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.61,0:08:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦  是我給挑選的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是實玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是我挑的  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會看走眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實  這是在春日強行加上的服裝中最頂級的貨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  超合適  這個給YES
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:58.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（YESだね：捏自Brain Power(機動神腦)的台詞）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是這個國家的古典民俗衣著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.19,0:09:05.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然胸口有點難受  不過好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就準備好了  那麼出發吧  去盆舞會場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過盆舞啊  感覺好像很久沒有看到過了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  實玖瑠  你想要玩的撈金魚也有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:29.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撈個痛快吧  黑色凸眼金魚可是加200分的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也去玩吧  來比比看能撈多少條如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:37.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我PASS  比起那個我還是對食物有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門你覺得如何  要吃點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對那種東西有興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  800日元
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:05.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,13條  雖然是大豐收但我不需要那麼多  就只要了一條
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是完全撈不起來  撈金魚好難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  正常人是撈不了那麼多的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.23,0:10:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有訣竅的話就很簡單了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  有希  那個面具是怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎…不過為什麼要這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是波長相合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因為是宇宙人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  不管了  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一塊還沒轉過  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只吃一個的話沒關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.34,0:11:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.39,0:11:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.12,0:11:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  盆舞也差不多跳完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來玩煙火吧  煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.37,0:11:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙火…嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.29,0:11:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得穿這身  今天就一起做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對  對面的店裡就有賣的  就去河邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很開心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柿崎！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（此處捏自「超時空要塞Macross」劇場版的柿崎機(VF-1A)）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.46,0:12:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盆舞  煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:12.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼明天是捉昆蟲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日啊  雖說玩也沒問題  你暑假作業做完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說一點也沒有動的我說這話有點那啥就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.86,0:12:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了  那種程度的作業有三天不就全部做完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.40,0:12:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我七月就解決掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:32.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種麻煩事就得事先趕緊收拾了  再毫無後顧之憂地玩到爽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是正確的享受暑假的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這種傢伙腦子這麼好  上天對於人的參數調整還真是隨便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:44.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之  明天去捉昆蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉到的蟲子最多的那個人…  這樣吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把團長的權力讓給他一天！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣呢  只要是蟲子的話什麼都可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:12:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…只能抓蟬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  這就是SOS團內部的捉蟬大戰  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只多抓了一隻也算贏！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了祈雨  我把晴天娃娃用五寸釘刺著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到來的卻是萬里無雲的好天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟬也為今年夏天最熱的一天而雀躍不已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  蟬能夠拿來吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許弄成天婦羅會是極品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.21,0:13:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我有時會想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天婦羅會不會只是外面一層麵衣好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  那蟬也可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快道歉！快向全國的天婦羅店道歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓青春年華的高中生拿著蟲網與籠子聚集在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有什麼企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊  沒有蟲網的話怎麼抓蟬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.65,0:13:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是問那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.87,0:14:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們開始了  優勝者可以當一天的團長！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.81,0:14:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒在聽…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的想贏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  捕蟬的話  小學不都試過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是啊  盡力而行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已經抓到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是蟬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海…海格力斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:36.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（大力神獨角仙(D.hercules)，胸部有大而光滑的角）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公佈結果！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠一隻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有希四隻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古泉七隻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛九隻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後最高紀錄是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  你不用說都知道是誰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我！十二隻！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  團長之座一天都讓不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家真是可惜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會真的想把它們做成天婦羅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  你想吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.78,0:15:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼成我要吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開個玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底  還是要有放生的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放它們一條生路  以後說不定會來報恩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快回山裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再被抓了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:15:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是說得好聽  但你這只是單方面的捕捉後放生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是接著的下一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日不知從何處找來了兼職
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還難得為我們爭取了機會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本地超市的紀念促銷宣傳活動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你們加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作內容是吸引顧客
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…連我都非得裝成這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是暑假的兼職
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有別的做法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且春日只是在一旁涼快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下來與她的日薪要是一樣的話  絕對要暴動的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於能明白脫皮後蛇的心情了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈  真是一個好例子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:16:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.44,0:17:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長大叔也謝謝大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要大叔的感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個囉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個外套就是工錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很早之前就很想要的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔也看在實玖瑠的份上說送給我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這隻青蛙要放在社團室裡當作紀念
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠  你想什麼時候穿都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我許可的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呱呱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳池  盂蘭盆節  捕蟲  兼職
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後春日進行的就是天體觀測
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  這就是這個年代的望遠鏡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與開普勒時代的沒什麼不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我覺得相差很遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是買來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我小時候的興趣就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看見木星衛星的時候真的十分激動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:17:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是火星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.55,0:18:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.68,0:18:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒不希望它存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章魚一樣的怪物蜿蜒地計劃著征服地球的圖像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要說好話我也不覺得有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.14,0:18:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是十分友好的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是在地下的大空洞偷偷地生活著的害羞人種
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓地球人感到吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你腦內的火星人到底有多麼文雅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來找UFO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.04,0:18:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在衛星軌道上  一定有異星人的先遣隊在待機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  實玖瑠也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…呃…UFO  UFO…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:18:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假還未結束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日接著要做的是——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:03.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到擊球中心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要到那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早看見甲子園的新聞我就想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能只滿足於那些雜牌的棒球比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們SOS團要建成以全國為目標的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那能量到底是從哪裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是細胞內的線粒體與常人不一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些能量能為世人用上一點就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.19,0:19:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後  誰也不能阻止春日定下的定額消耗態勢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不停地跟著行動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:19:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也去了真正的煙火大會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也將砰砰地射上高空\N又碰碰地綻放的煙火觀賞到滿足為止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在另一天  我們則在縣邊境的河邊參加釣蝦虎魚大會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  實玖瑠  竿子竿子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧  我會拿回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下還有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是固定節目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但應該沒有人真會去玩的試膽大會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看了只有宣傳非常像那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.14,0:20:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但內容大家都心知肚明的大製作電影的聯播
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在完全是淡季的會漂來水母的海灘上進行海水浴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.62,0:20:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到所有人都達到全清才能離開的保齡球懲罰遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:21:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑戰喉嚨極限的長時間耐久卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:11.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至覺得包括了很多與夏天無關的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  我們在這兩週內玩到再起不能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是8月30日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課題都完成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀唉呀  總算順利完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…這樣就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…嗯  也就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還有什麼想做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.62,0:21:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.34,0:21:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想好好睡一覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.84,0:21:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有希呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.83,0:21:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好  這個夏天都幹了不少事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四處遊玩  也穿上了浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟬也抓了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.52,0:21:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就到這裡為止吧  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.28,0:22:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這傢伙還有什麼遺憾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.05,0:22:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼今天就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就空下來當是預備日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.04,0:22:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好好地休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後天再在社團教室見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.50,0:22:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊  作業完全沒有做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8月31日  暑假的最後一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正怎麼努力都不可能把作業做完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.69,0:22:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒法消除玩後的疲勞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.94,0:22:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就這樣子拖拖拉拉地過了懶散的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.67,0:23:00.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.79,0:23:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.29,0:23:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管了  由它去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡吧  明天還要上學
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.32,0:23:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關燈睡覺


